{"type":null,"faqId":49820,"title":"手机没有信号","answer":"<p id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264496__li11855130\">\n<p id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264496__p47562882165430\">以下几种情况可能导致手机无信号：</p>\n<ul id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264496__ul20122415\">\n  <li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264496__li62510672165427\" style=\"list-style-type: disc;\">无法识别 SIM/UIM 卡：\n  <p id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264496__p24703359165533\">1、请确认手机是否可以识别插入的 SIM/UIM 卡，不同网络制式的手机支持的SIM/UIM卡类型不同，具体请咨询手机提供商。</p>\n  <p id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264496__p21003643165533\">2、请查看手机状态栏图标是否显示为无卡标识，如显示为无卡标识，请参考随机附送的快速指南，检查是否正确地插入了 SIM/UIM 卡。</p>\n  <p id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264496__p54815059165533\">3、请确认 SIM/UIM 卡是否有效。将 SIM/UIM 卡插入其他手机中查看是否可正常使用。</p>\n  <p id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264496__p23573490165533\">4、如SIM/UIM 卡为剪卡，请前往营业厅更换标准的SIM/UIM 卡后尝试。</p>\n  </li>\n  <li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264496__li2337129\" style=\"list-style-type: disc;\">无网络信号：\n  <p id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264496__p21034167\">可能是当前网络信号差导致手机无信号，请等待一段时间或到信号较好的地方使用手机。</p>\n  </li>\n  <li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264496__li55089778\" style=\"list-style-type: disc;\">SIM/UIM 卡被停用：\n  <p id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264496__p46425733113012\">对于双卡手机，请点击<span class=\"menucascade\" id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264496__menucascade3717315911300\">“<span class=\"uicontrol\" id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264496__uicontrol6612298111300\">设置</span> &gt; <span class=\"uicontrol\" id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264496__uicontrol5823591811300\">双卡管理</span>”</span>，确认 SIM/UIM 卡是否已启用。</p>\n  </li>\n  <li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264496__li33087003\" style=\"list-style-type: disc;\">飞行模式误开启：\n  <p id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264496__p29347571\">请确认手机未开启飞行模式。飞行模式开启后，状态栏中显示飞行模式图标，此时手机会没有信号。</p>\n  </li>\n</ul>\n<p id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264496__p46884008\">若以上几项检查后依然无信号，请重启手机。</p>\n<p id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264496__p19302893\">若重启后问题依然存在，请联系客服或携带购机发票前往服务网点检修。</p>\n</p>\n<div>\n<div class=\"familylinks\"></div>\n</div>","faqTypeId":144,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"zh-cn_topic_0022264496","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1448615544000,"seriesProductName":"NXT-AL10A,NXT-AL10B,NXT-AL10C,NXT-CL00A,NXT-DL00A,NXT-TL00A","visitedTimes":186,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"没有信号","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}